The '''Secret Treasure of the Jedi''' was a rumored treasure hidden by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] within the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple's]] basement. Despite its vast value, it was contained within a small, handheld box.

[[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] used the rumor of this treasure to lure [[Vilmarh Grahrk]] into helping him with the [[Yinchorri Uprising]]. Palpatine may have stolen it during the [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] [[Raid on the Jedi Temple (Yinchorri Uprising)|attack]] on the Temple. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] also had heard rumors of large amounts of treasure being hidden in the Temple.

While accompanying [[Ferus Olin]] in breaking into the Jedi Temple [[Trever Flume]] was another who believed that the treasure indeed existed; however Ferus dismissed the rumor as propaganda.

